{"tid":1392744,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警察同解放軍，你企邊一邊？","createTime":"2019-08-01T00:18:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T00:26:26.000Z","uid":50457,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ae7c654a530f7874d8bc8b5160dec269d9e0149b","tid":1392744,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T00:18:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d482ac2049b0d2a3b051f1b469cb4f5c3869abbf","tid":1392744,"uid":9193,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T00:18:52.000Z","msg":"兩邊都唔企"},{"pid":"6b957718a4f3572a7818018dcaa579d07fb7df45","tid":1392744,"uid":215876,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T00:20:02.000Z","msg":"兩邊打飽去<br />\n但佢地 應該fd過夾band"},{"pid":"f5d467aeafd6898fbedd803ce88a43c8c7412671","tid":1392744,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T00:20:31.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n首先釋放義士<br />\n撤回送中法案<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">即時進行雙真普選<br />\n由民選政府組織獨立調查委員會徹查</span></span>"},{"pid":"a4edbaa565b77c16ac6987e67603460877543b52","tid":1392744,"uid":18395,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T00:21:26.000Z","msg":"佢地一家親 點會打<br />\n垃圾post 咪推"},{"pid":"c89c5160b81737daa219b127d4c94f406386ac49","tid":1392744,"uid":272976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T00:22:41.000Z","msg":"等佢哋狗咬狗"},{"pid":"896e6c97be1f01ce096120222cdd4334d8df7442","tid":1392744,"uid":153418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T00:23:30.000Z","msg":"睇下邊面人工高"},{"pid":"a65adb9eacc41a75842b190650d0f0c88c4ac625","tid":1392744,"uid":4575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T00:23:40.000Z","msg":"我企後邊"},{"pid":"508e6970a3347dc99ab83e2e5034e06786677c2d","tid":1392744,"uid":2419,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T00:23:42.000Z","msg":"痴線 唔鍾意警察都唔會企老解果邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9360c4719ed7af17f86f0c302da3d74f1b9ae4a","tid":1392744,"uid":6528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T00:25:10.000Z","msg":"全民8月5日大罷工！五大訴求，缺一不可！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雙普選一定要排最頭，仲要好似美國咁設時限係2020年內落實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全民黑衫、口罩同頭盔，返工返學行街，唔擺工既日子一齊做，將抗爭帶入生活，保護示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379839\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379839</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n當新移民夠多，雙普選自然會落實，港共明顯會用偽民主反真港人<br />\n（雖然係舊post，但都想人諗下，一定要止左血先）<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1328467\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1328467</a><br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n想比更多人知道其實而家呢一刻基本上得番<span style=\"color: gold;\">香港獨立</span>呢條路，<br />\n我知好多人未準備好，我知而家急唔黎。<br />\n但係想大家思考下，種下一個思想，唔好屌我住。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家就算有真普選其實都係under中共！！<br />\n咁唔通去到2047再抗爭過咩，西方國家都出唔到手幫你地。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為白紙黑字寫明50年，西方國家唔好話出手，連發聲既正當性都冇啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能好多前人都係到諗點解英國當時唔寫999年！<br />\n可能好多我地呢代既諗點解上一代冇去抗爭！<br />\n可能好多下一代係2047係到諗點解我地唔直接爭取獨立！！！<br />\n<br />\n我地唔可以好似上一代咁，計好哂數50年後都死左啦，唔好理啦。<br />\n我地唔可以再咁自私啦，過埋2047都嗰頭近啦，之後再算啦。<br />\n我想我地既下一代唔需要再為呢啲事再受苦啦，我只係希望下一代可以係呼吸住自由既空氣出世係呢個地球上。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有既問題，所有既恩怨，係我地呢代到解決哂啦，好嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所有問題去到最後只會追究到主權問題，希望大家思考下。<br />\n今次搞到咁大真係最後一次反擊同最大力量。<br />\n<br />\nBTW，五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n雙普選應要排最頭，仲要設時限，最好2020年內！"},{"pid":"757465f54662229da1a67421adbf74f87b6de17f","tid":1392744,"uid":253037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T00:25:14.000Z","msg":"唔好諗住出老解<br />\n我地同狗有得connect啊<br />\n<br />\n無一隻狗係無辜架"},{"pid":"a706d542b8ae3d17925356dd17041bb796bd7025","tid":1392744,"uid":31094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T00:26:26.000Z","msg":"狗仔隨時揪贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}